## Multi-agent / parallel work safety

- Assume multiple agents may modify the repo in parallel.
- Keep changes minimal and focused; avoid unrelated refactors.
- Avoid noisy churn (mass formatting/reserialization/lockfile churn) unless explicitly required.
- If unrelated changes are present, split them by task/concern and commit separately.

